Day 23: 

Masterpiece

I will paint your scars
Of the past into a masterpiece
I will chip away at the
Brick walls around your heart
Until every ounce of love is freed

I will whisper poetry of
Love in your ear until
You feel that love brim forth
And sketch our future
Gently across your skin

I will sing soothingly to you
Until the sunshine returns to your smile
I will hold you close so
Our hearts will beat in unison

I will look at you adoringly
As if you are a work of art
That belongs in a museum
 I will see your imperfections
And realize they make you priceless

I will love you
In the only way
An artist can
With everything I am
I was happy to hear your voice ð¥°
